default 
default&#xa0;
defaultAfter meeting with senior Israeli and Palestinian trade unionists in Israel and the West Bank, Guy Ryder said ‘with the pea
defaultce process effectively in stalemate at present, the ITUC’s working together with our Israeli and Palestinian affiliates is especially important.’
